'''[[ectopic]] [[pregnancy]]'''
#a [[pregnancy]] in which the [[fertilize]]d [[ovum]] is implanted in any tissue other than the [[uterus|uterine]] wall. Most ectopic pregnancies occur in the [[Fallopian tube]] (so-called [[tubal pregnancies]]), but implantation can also occur in the [[cervix]], [[ovary|ovaries]], and [[abdomen]].